<div><div id='zzqkl3lf4cnapgcRiverDetailGadget2' class='CRiverDetailGadget-detail CRiverDetailGadget'><div class='controls'><h1>Silver - B) 'Lower Silver': Arvon Rd to Silver Falls Park (4.2 miles)</h1>
<div><div id='zzqkl3lf4cnapgcArticleGadget26Container' class='CArticleGadget-view CArticleGadget'><div id='zzqkl3lf4cnapgcArticleGadget26-1' class='contents'></div></div> <br style='clear:both'>
</div>
